Canadian actor Jonathan Crombie died on Wednesday night in New York after suffering a brain hemorrhage .
The actor is best known for his role as Gilbert Blythe in the Canadian television drama film Anne of Green Gables and two sequels .
He was discovered at 17 when he was performing in The Wizard of Oz .
Crombie was the son for former Toronto mayor and Canadian Cabinet minister David Crombie , never screen-tested for the show .